        "description": "<p>To our community: We are excited to present you the results of our 2021 open competition with the Facult of Fine Arts at the University of Lisbon. We invited all students to submit their original designs for a chance to work with us and showcase their talents to the world.<br/><br/>We were blown away by the creativity and passion of the students who participated in this competition. After careful consideration, YOU chose Joana Brigida (with Feel) and Maria João Estevão (with Rethink) as the winners of this contest. And their designs are now available.</p>",
