        "section_sub": "",
        "description": "<p>This collaboration has allowed us to stay close to national talents and up-to-date with current trends while providing students with valuable business tools. The jury composed of members of the Fine Arts faculty and Paez team judged the 10 best submissions, but the final decision was left to the public. We are grateful for your participation in this process.<br/><br/>We are honoured to showcase these unique and meaningful designs to our Paez community and hope that you will enjoy wearing them as much as we saw the thrill in Joana and Maria João throughout this whole process.</p>",
